Catherine Cusack https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Catherine_Cusack 0 Catherine Cusack (born 21 December 1968, in London) is an English actress of Irish descent, best known for portraying Nanny Carmel Finnan in long-running ITV soap opera Coronation Street in 1992 and 1993.
